---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Container } from "@/components/layout/Container";
import HeroImage from "../components/ui/HeroImage.astro";
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<Layout
    title="Starting a Daycare | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Your daycare business starts with understanding what makes your market unique. Get personalized insights based on your state's regulations and market conditions."
>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <HeroImage
                src="/images/startup/starting-a-daycare.webp"
                alt="Modern daycare facility interior illustrating the successful result of following the steps to opening a childcare center"
                className="mb-4 md:mb-12"
            />
            <div class="text-center">
                <span class="pro-text-meta mb-2 block">
                    Getting Started
                </span>
                <h1 class="text-xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6">
                    YOUR Daycare Business
                </h1>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    Starting a daycare isn't a one-size-fits-all journey. Your state, your capacity, and your market create a unique opportunity that generic advice can't capture.
                </p>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- FACTORS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section bg-gray-50/50">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card mb-3 md:mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    What Affects Your Success
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        Every daycare operates under different conditions that dramatically impact both startup costs and income potential. Your state's licensing requirements might allow you to care for 6 children or 12. Your local regulations might require extensive renovations or minimal changes.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        These variables aren't just details—they're the foundation of your business model. A home daycare in Vermont operates under completely different constraints than a center in Texas.
                    </p>
                    <p class="hidden md:block">
                        Beyond regulations, your local competition, demographic composition, and even zoning laws create opportunities and limitations unique to your situation.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- WHY GENERIC FAILS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Why Online Advice Often Conflicts
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        You've probably noticed that every article about starting a daycare tells a different story. One says you need $50,000 to start, another says $5,000. Both are right—for someone.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Generic advice assumes conditions that might be completely different from yours. Personalization isn't a luxury—it's a necessity. You need to see the numbers for your state, your capacity, and your market.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card text-center border-2 border-teal-200/50 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/20 to-white/50">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-4">
                    See How Much YOU Could Make
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 mb-3 md:mb-6">
                    Get your personalized income estimate based on your state's regulations and your business model.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/#calculator"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-bold px-5 py-2 md:px-8 md:py-4 shadow-lg transition-all text-xs md:text-base group"
                >
                    Use the Free Calculator
                    <ArrowRight className="w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>
</Layout>
